{"word":"λύπη","slug":"λύπη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>λύπη, ης, ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>] ‘inner distress’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on mental or spiritual aspect <b>grief, sorrow <a href='B:490 22:45'>Lk 22:45</a>; <a href='B:500 16:6'>J 16:6</a>, <a href='B:500 16:20'>20</a>, <a href='B:500 16:22'>22</a>; <a href='B:520 9:2'>Ro 9:2</a>; <a href='B:540 2:1'>2 Cor 2:1</a>, <a href='B:540 2:3'>3</a>, <a href='B:540 2:7'>7</a>; <a href='B:540 7:10'>7:10</a>; <a href='B:540 9:7'>9:7</a>; <a href='B:570 2:27'>Phil 2:27</a>; <a href='B:650 12:11'>Hb 12:11</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on associated physical aspect, <b>pain</b> in birthing <b><a href='B:500 16:21'>J 16:21</a>;</b> in persecution <b><a href='B:670 2:19'>1 Pt 2:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λυπέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Λυσανίας\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}